title: Unisonic Ascension - Hreeh Chanting Delta [FLAC]
description:
The Hreeh chanting, is an Ambient Dharma choir, made by several layers. Hreeh transforms sadness into compassion, appreciation, and gratitude by removing the feeling of loss, separation, and longing from the frequency of sadness. There is a 3D pink noise spiral whirl in the background so that more of the brain is involved in the chant and healing frequencies. The binaural beats pattern is moving in the Delta range of 4Hz.& 2Hz. There is also pulsed isochronic pink noise, to allow the composition to useful by headphones or through speakers.
